{"tid":691640,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[好撚痛]唔聽阿媽話偷走去游水 巴西少年遭鯊咬噬下體亡","createTime":"2018-06-06T02:45:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T15:27:24.000Z","uid":76329,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"336c06af360c6e3d61edcad6a46366691181bb0c","tid":691640,"uid":76329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T02:45:52.000Z","msg":"巴西伯南布哥州累西腓一名18歲少年，周日（3日）無視母親和救生員警告，到一個有鯊魚出沒的海灘游泳，結果陰莖和左方股骨遭鯊魚狂噬，最終失血過多而亡。死者母親收到噩耗後哭成淚人，聞者心酸。<br />\n<br />\n達席爾瓦（Jose Ferreira da Silva）當日下午與兄弟及友人，在當地一個海灘的深水區暢泳。救生員指深水區有鯊魚出沒，着他們返回淺水區，言畢達席爾瓦即遭鯊魚襲擊。由泳客拍攝片段可見，救生員及泳客將他救上岸，傷口不斷滲出血水，場面駭人。<br />\n<br />\n當局表示，達席爾瓦下體及左股骨遭虎鯊噬掉，被送院搶救，最終失血過多不治。其母抵達醫院後痛哭，指曾叮囑兒子不要游泳，後者卻不聽勸告，趁她外出工作時偷偷跑出去，最終賠上性命。在4月，事發海灘一名34歲泳客被鯊魚襲擊，一手一腳被噬。"},{"pid":"dc0ad6e2e39ac69d2986327ae4a620c784b322b3","tid":691640,"uid":83679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T11:27:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1602144ad6065f27936e6c889b873b0408fb9f74","tid":691640,"uid":24623,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T11:29:00.000Z","msg":"圓呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64f8bfb3f6f9bb20f56e7efc6d1f260fb9b92d34","tid":691640,"uid":24623,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T11:29:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">圖</span>呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2524822fdf245b3cbe305a0c3c925813e886cd85","tid":691640,"uid":182334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T11:30:10.000Z","msg":"㘣呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00841eca5793be384efe34f5a87aa2d0acbf6229","tid":691640,"uid":54684,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T11:35:35.000Z","msg":"救樓主<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-5809669/Lifeguards-race-shark-infested-waters-rescue-Brazilian-teen-penis-bitten-off.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-5809669%2FLifeguards-race-shark-infested-waters-rescue-Brazilian-teen-penis-bitten-off.html&d=kEmSxAroJEq%2Bdf0fzaYk5cVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=7e689c68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-5809669/Lifeguards-race-shark-infested-waters-rescue-Brazilian-teen-penis-bitten-off.html</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\nDailyMail有影片  但傷口打格仔"},{"pid":"f90a6a9d2e7aa720b80b2956932c95e47060a9fc","tid":691640,"uid":143288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T11:42:53.000Z","msg":"聽媽媽的話"},{"pid":"faaa626c75d89770995c7e2a22fc0b69a82ad4b8","tid":691640,"uid":67462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T11:49:25.000Z","msg":"條鯊魚真係識食"},{"pid":"ed03b4402bdc92d553a02258c30e86b94c63f818","tid":691640,"uid":60787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T12:13:42.000Z","msg":"咬J魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf714a708d2a20a469a9a3edfdd88af0fd021884","tid":691640,"uid":82068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T15:18:54.000Z","msg":"個腦海想像到有條大白鯊係海底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對住條撚樣<br />\n一下鳩衝衝上水面咬到條撚樣人j分離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da44d29fa9d0e6c5e2e603705643d394a8e577ca","tid":691640,"uid":1724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T15:21:55.000Z","msg":"含撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fd41f11c52dd95a411f21f3900da5803209f32a","tid":691640,"uid":64571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T15:27:24.000Z","msg":"好彩死撚咗<br />\n唔死仲慘過死"}]}